cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL. 

The paper is about scene segmentation, which is a computer vision task, so cs.CV is the most likely category. The paper also introduces a new module for feature learning, which falls under the category of machine learning, so cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely categories. The paper uses a data-driven approach to infer contextual dependencies, which involves neural networks, so cs.NE is another likely category. Finally, the paper deals with natural language processing to some extent, as it mentions context-aware feature learning, so cs.CL is a less likely but still possible category.
